OL,3,CNew world record hope for man who
OL,4,Chelped restore iconic Bluebird
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Paul
OL,7,FCrone went to meet Dave Aldred and see
OL,8,Fhis latest project
OL,10,FThe man who helped restore the iconic
OL,11,FBluebird watercraft is hoping to make
OL,12,Fhistory himself - by breaking the
OL,13,Fworld water speed record.
OL,15,FDave Aldred has spent years rebuilding
OL,16,Fthe ill-fated high-speed craft which
OL,17,Fwas lost to the bottom of Coniston
OL,18,FWater in the Lake District after it
OL,19,Fsomersaulted and crashed during a
OL,20,Frecord attempt in 1967, killing pilot
OL,21,FDonald Campbell instantly.
