OL,3,CNew world record hope for man who
OL,4,Chelped restore iconic Bluebird
OL,6,FAlongside the mammoth project he has
OL,7,Falso been designing his own
OL,8,Fhydroplane, Longbow, with hopes it can
OL,9,Fbreak the current 317.59 mph record,
OL,10,Fset in Australia in 1978.
OL,12,FThe twin-engine craft is being built
OL,13,Fin Dave's Thornton workshop in
OL,14,FLancashire before the record attempt
OL,15,Fin Coniston.
OL,17,F"We're doing it just an hour up the
OL,18,Froad at Coniston, so it's very real,
OL,19,Fthe public can come and see it," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
