OL,3,CNew world record hope for man who
OL,4,Chelped restore iconic Bluebird
OL,6,F"There aren't many records that you
OL,7,Fcan do that, that are outright
OL,8,Frecords, the fastest in the world."
OL,10,FHe says he is aware of the risks
OL,11,FLongbow's pilot Lt. David-John Gibbs
OL,12,FRN will face at such high speeds.
OL,14,F"You've no suspension, there could be
OL,15,Fthings it the water, you've got gusts
OL,16,Fcoming down off the mountains and the
OL,17,Ftrick is to keep the boat skimming
OL,18,Facross the water without taking off or
OL,19,Fgoing in," he added.
