OL,3,CNew world record hope for man who
OL,4,Chelped restore iconic Bluebird
OL,6,FDave and his small team of dedicated
OL,7,Fexperts are hoping to bring the world
OL,8,Fwater speed record back to Britain
OL,10,F"Donald couldn't even see to some
OL,11,Fextent, he was getting eyeball
OL,12,Foscillation," Dave said.
OL,14,F"Now with Longbow she's an air
OL,15,Ftrapping hull, so that's a bit
OL,16,Fdifferent, she skims across the water
OL,17,Fmuch better, but it's something else,
OL,18,Fit's horrendously quick."
OL,20,FLongbow is likely to undergo trials in
OL,21,FScottish lochs and at Coniston.
